name: The Remix of the Remix of a Misunderstanding of Rarity Driven By Speculative Capitalists Dressed In Sheep's Clothing pt1
description: I was told that my commentary on PFP's was invaluable, but they didn't like the platform chosen for the critique. But that's fine, I can just make this one unique in no time so that the value is locked in and guaranteed. There are many like it but this one is yours.
